    communityDescription: 'The Green River Valley stretches from Auburn up through Kent, a working landscape with deep roots — farmland, warehouses, small-acreage properties, and the river itself winding through it all. The Green River Natural Resources Area, the Green River Trail, and the remnants of the Lower Green River Agricultural Production District keep the valley\'s farming heritage alive even as the land around it has filled in.',
